{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":3,"text":"1. SDK 是否支持 Objective-C，是否有 Objective-C 文档？","anchor":"1-SDK-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-Objective-C%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%9C%89-Objective-C-%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SDK 使用 Swift 开发，但也支持 Objective-C 调用。"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"DocC 文档支持 Objective-C，但是 DocC 生成的静态托管仅包含 Swift 接口，Objective-C 内容不会在静态网站中呈现。若需要查看 Objective-C 内容，请在 macos 中查看"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"2. SDK 可以在多线程中调用吗？支持并发发送命令吗？","anchor":"2-SDK-%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%AD%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%90%97%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E5%8F%91%E9%80%81%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%90%97","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"可以在后台线程中调用，但不支持并发发送命令。","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"SDK 中大部分方法为阻塞调用，建议放在后台线程中执行，以避免阻塞主线程。","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"需要注意的是，设备模块一次只能处理一条命令，因此不要在多个线程中同时发送多条命令。"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"推荐在同一个后台线程中按顺序调用多个命令，而不是在多个线程中并发调用。"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"3. RFID 标签数据为什么通常显示为十六进制？可以存储 ASCII 字符吗？","anchor":"3-RFID-%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%BA%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8-ASCII-%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%97","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"在 SDK 中，标签数据通常以十六进制字符串的形式展示或传输，这是为了便于查看和处理底层数据。","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"如果需要保存 ASCII 字符，可以先将字符串按 ASCII 编码转换为对应的十六进制字符串，再将该十六进制字符串保存到 RFID 标签中。","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"读取或盘点到标签数据时，再将该十六进制数据还原为 ASCII 字符串，从而实现 ASCII 内容的存储与读取。"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"4. 为什么连接蓝牙时会出现“蓝牙配对请求”的弹窗？需要点击配对还是取消？可以取消这个弹窗吗？","anchor":"4-%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E8%93%9D%E7%89%99%E6%97%B6%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%93%9D%E7%89%99%E9%85%8D%E5%AF%B9%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%B9%E7%AA%97%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E9%85%8D%E5%AF%B9%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E5%BC%B9%E7%AA%97%E5%90%97","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"蓝牙配对请求.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"这个弹窗是 iOS 系统弹出的。由于设备包含键盘服务，iOS 会将设备识别为键盘，并尝试与其直接配对，以便后续自动连接。","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"对于这个弹窗，建议点击取消。如果选择了配对，设备会与 iOS 系统建立连接，这会带来一些问题。比如设备一旦与系统建立连接，APP 在执行断开连接时，只能进行 APP 层面的断开，而无法让设备与系统断开连接。在未与系统断开连接的情况下，搜索蓝牙时将无法找到该设备，因为设备已经处于连接状态。"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"这个弹窗可以取消。出现弹窗的原因在于设备存在键盘服务，iOS 会将其识别为键盘，因此只要关闭键盘服务即可。需要注意，蓝牙版本 2.10 及以上才支持关闭键盘服务，并且关闭后，HID 服务将不再可用。"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"如果想取消这个弹窗，首先在 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"系统设置->蓝牙"},{"type":"text","text":" 中忽略已配对的设备，然后按照以下步骤操作："}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"在 APP 中连接设备，切换到蓝牙设置，点击获取按钮获取当前蓝牙配置"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"关掉“蓝牙绑定属性”和“HID键盘服务”选项"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"点击设置按钮。设置成功后设备会断开蓝牙并重启，这是正常现象"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"若是还出现弹窗，重新连接设备，点击“删除绑定设备”按钮"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"ble-settings-zh.png","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"这篇文章主要介绍一些使用 RFIDManager 可能会遇到的常见问题","type":"text"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFIDManager----","doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/tutorials\/--RFIDManager","doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFID-----"],"title":"中文文档","anchor":"中文文档","generated":true}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"RFIDManager"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"RFIDManager 常见问题"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager"],["doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager","doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFIDManager----"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFIDManager-----","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/rfidmanager\/rfidmanager-----"]}],"references":{"ble-settings-zh.png":{"identifier":"ble-settings-zh.png","alt":"蓝牙设置页面中取消匹配弹窗操作示例","type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/ble-settings-zh.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"蓝牙配对请求.png":{"identifier":"蓝牙配对请求.png","alt":"蓝牙配对请求","type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/%E8%93%9D%E7%89%99%E9%85%8D%E5%AF%B9%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://com.rfid.RFIDManager/documentation/RFIDManager/RFID-----":{"role":"article","title":"RFID 基本知识","abstract":[{"text":"本文主要介绍 RFID 相关的基础知识，帮助你更好地了解 RFIDManager 库","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFID-----","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/rfidmanager\/rfid-----"},"doc://com.rfid.RFIDManager/tutorials/--RFIDManager":{"role":"overview","title":"初识 RFIDManager","abstract":[{"text":"这个教程将展示如何将 RFIDManager 库导入到您的项目中，并简单介绍如何使用它","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/tutorials\/--RFIDManager","type":"topic","kind":"overview","url":"\/tutorials\/--rfidmanager"},"doc://com.rfid.RFIDManager/documentation/RFIDManager/RFIDManager----":{"url":"\/documentation\/rfidmanager\/rfidmanager----","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[{"text":"Apple 全平台的 RFID 标签读写管理框架","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"RFIDManager 中文文档","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFIDManager----"},"doc://com.rfid.RFIDManager/documentation/RFIDManager":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A framework for RFID tag reading, writing, and management on Apple platforms.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager","title":"RFIDManager","url":"\/documentation\/rfidmanager","type":"topic"}}}